    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Mind sphere (Vision (charm)), caster level 10th.</p>\n<p>As a greater charm, you may spend 2 spell points to give the target a vision of the most fearsome creature imaginable, pulling its subconscious fears into a shape before its eyes. Only the target can see this vision, although you may see the vague shape of the creature the target is seeing. The target first gets a Will save to recognize the image as unreal. If that save fails, the phantasm touches the subject, and the subject must succeed on a Fortitude save or die from fear. This is a fear effect.</p>\n",
